WEBVTT

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:42.000
指はるかに胸にきけば If I listen with my finger far in my chest

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:51.800
心はかえる楽しむかし My heart is happy and joyful

00:00:51.800 --> 00:01:08.600
Ah, sing, oh you, sing for ever

00:01:08.600 --> 00:01:21.600
胸懐かし君歌え I miss you so much, I sing for you

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:37.600
歌え歌え後に Sing, sing, after you

00:01:38.600 --> 00:01:54.600
明日やむつくもののとく Tomorrow, I will be happy and joyful

00:01:55.600 --> 00:02:08.600
君が曖昧の歌う見れば The future you see is so clear

00:02:09.600 --> 00:02:19.600
