00:02:19.600 --> 00:02:31.600
Ah, sing, oh you, sing for ever

00:02:31.600 --> 00:02:41.600
またもまたも歌え I miss you so much, I sing for you

00:02:41.600 --> 00:02:51.600
懐かし君へ 歌えよ Sing, sing, after you

00:02:51.600 --> 00:03:09.600
歌えよ 歌えよ あなたへ 歌えよ Sing, sing, after you

